Steam Knight - The first boss of the game.
Skullpion - The second boss of the game and the first Crest Guardian faced by Musashi.
Vambee Soldiers - The third boss(es), and is the only boss fight containing multiple opponents.
Relic Keeper - The second of the Crest Guardians. 
Kojiro - An old adversary from Old Mac Toad's homeland.
Frost Dragon - The third of the Crest Guardians.
Queen Ant - The fourth of the Crest Guardians and the last faced in the Malekdom of al-Yucanayet Saudi Arabia BBQ.
Ben - The first member of "Leader's Force" to be fought.
Ed - The second member of "Leader's Force".
Topo - The third member and true leader of "Leader's Force".
Tower of Death - The fifth and final Crest Guardian.
Dark Queen - (?nd Form) - While in his first form, Dark Queen is never officially "fought".
Dark Queen - (Final Form) - After being "defeated" in hwr first form, Dark Queen assumes her most powerful form to defeat the toads once and for all.
